<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-MCw98/SFnGE8fJT3GXwEOngsV7Zt27NXFoaoApmYm81iuXoPkFOJwJ8ERdknLPMO" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> 
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="heading">
   <div class="title"><div class="logo"><img src="../img/eanqekla_0.png" alt=""></div><h1>ShortenURL</h1></div><p>ShortenURL is a tool that helps reduce long links from Instagram, Facebook, YouTube, Twitter, Linked In and top sites on the Internet! Just paste the long URL and click the Shorten button. After shortening the URL, you can even track the number of clicks.
</p></div>
   <form action="/shortUrls" method="POST" >
    <label for="fullUrl" class="sr-only">Enter URL here</label>
    <input type="url" name = "fullUrl" id = "fullUrl" required placeholder="Enter your URL here">
    <button type="submit">Shorten</button>
   </form>

   <table class="table table-striped ">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th scope="col" class="removable">Full URL</th>
        <th scope="col">Short URL </th>
        <th scope="col">Clicks</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% shortUrls.forEach(shortUrl => {%>
        <tr>
          <td class="removable"><a href="<%= shortUrl.full %>"><%= shortUrl.full %></a> </td>
          <td><a href="<%= shortUrl.short%>"><%= shortUrl.short%></a></td>
          <td style="color:#D62AD0"><%= shortUrl.clicks%></td>
        </tr>
      <%})%>
    
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

</body>
</html>